  Locus:
    Page: 341
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Oneness
---
All life is one. Differences are superficial. They are only in the outer;
they are only in the body. But one great common Consciousness dwells as the
Reality within all names and forms, with all creatures, not only all human
beings, in all creatures.
